        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2018-05-24 23:20:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nI discussed this with Amir at one point, and I thought the conclusion was that we would remove the deprecation warning from \"lctl list_nids\" and instead replace the back-end functionality in lctl with the equivalent of \"lnetctl net show\", and do the YAML parsing to present equivalent output as \"lctl list_nids\"?\n\nThat avoids breaking all of the scripts that may use \"lctl list_nids\", while allowing the command to continue working as changes are being made to the LNet user interface.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "f32ec08336cd380546c9bbbd57465347c16c2de2",
